ml&d=rAQnac8JMVWt93r0A5DTV3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5289256e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180903/bkn-20180903112718478-0903_00822_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:24:08.000Z","msg":"抵啦 乜都唔洗做 人工又高"},{"pid":"6aa73a6d3f583b1d7b26c4868b66983b0c4ae785","tid":804871,"uid":183248,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"664c2c9d7dd446aac3dcb02dd88f7d03866b5694","tid":804871,"uid":83060,"like":26,"dislike":69,"score":-43,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"呢個行業根本唔值呢個價，全體減薪三份之二就差不多。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"aafecbbe1495ef82051239a394513e205c6a5bb4","tid":804871,"uid":23402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲啲又要考多個牌了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532b3826eadb568039ebe58cdcaf1db4585e6da0","tid":804871,"uid":41846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:33:33.000Z","msg":"真係好能慘<br />\n平時都畀人當狗撚，加下做到出事<br />\n之後過多兩日冇人記得<br />\n<br />\n政府出嚟廢吹幾句&gt;&gt;&gt;又話多啲關注&gt;&gt;&gt;過多個月&gt;&gt;&gt;康文cut福利&gt;&gt;&gt;判頭又撳價&gt;&gt;&gt;當狗咁撚，廉價勞工不斷循環"},{"pid":"fc5481a6bed00045f38ed61589eb9f5719e97980","tid":804871,"uid":172321,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f7d7a1e140223d9dbb6f847832697c53afc7cbbd","tid":804871,"uid":74033,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:19:47.000Z","msg":"40歲仲做緊季節性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做唔到長工<br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T12:36:55.000Z","msg":"冬天沙灘係會休季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叻唔切"},{"pid":"905a8d0748f6c3bdc1411c8b39c9bf7669ce6088","tid":804871,"uid":3197,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"49f1145e73728f78947ce29